# semiperimeter

- _semiperimeter(g)_

Answer the semiperimeter of the geometry _g_.

The semiperimeter of a polygon is half its perimeter:

```
>>> let t = sssTriangle(3, 4, 5);
>>> (t.semiperimeter, t.perimeter)
(6, 12)

>>> (3 + 4 + 5) / 2
6
```

